Dagmar Dahlgren https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dagmar_Dahlgren 0 Dagmar Dahlgren (January 17, 1880 - October 20, 1951) was a dancer, singer and motion picture actress of the silent film era from Los Angeles, California. She had a brief career in motion pictures from 1920-1922.
